>f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">g</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↦</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∘</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ω</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↦</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ω</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">g</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ω</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rfl</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rw</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">this</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">←</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">map_map_of_aemeasurable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">measurable_mul</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">aemeasurable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">AEMeasurable</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">prodMk</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hg</span><span class=\"o\">),</span>\n<span class=\"w\">     </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">indepFun_iff_map_prod_eq_prod_map_map</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hf</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hg</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">mp</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">hfg</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">rfl</span>\n\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">indepFun</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
